{"tid":968211,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟係咪我做錯 我唔著","createTime":"2019-01-04T05:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T10:55:57.000Z","uid":192325,"like":0,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2a1ea4d14781ab232f7445ea8f0e1e0fbfa7e2da","tid":968211,"uid":192325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:10:17.000Z","msg":"拍咗半年拖 一直都好sweet<br />\n佢成日比surprise佢 我話想要咩<br />\n佢都會偷偷地買送比我<br />\n我每次都好開心 話佢好傻 係咪on9嫁真係買比我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢一直都冇講自己想要咩 我又冇咩錢買 所以心裏面一直都欠左佢咁<br />\n<br />\n到咗最近 我成日要返工好忙 有好多野要做<br />\n冇乜時間見面 咁就大家番工去到24號先見<br />\n原來佢準備左我一直想要既野比我 同埋帶我去食好西 但我咩都冇買 可能一直都冇點慶祝同埋最近真係好忙 佢同我講我冇送唔緊要 但其實我都好大壓力 我咩都冇送過比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過心入面睇得出既有少少失落 始終第一年過聖誕<br />\n<br />\n不過到呢家我都冇買聖誕禮物比佢 因為我真係惗唔到，<strong>但佢就覺得我唔愛佢</strong>因爲第一年過聖誕 竟然咩都冇準備 最重要係佢知道我上年同ex有慶祝但同佢就咩都冇準備 <br />\n<br />\n其實我真係好忙好忙先冇準備 究竟係咪我錯我唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb2e95b3fe4310656a5b82b310f76c3fbae0c40","tid":968211,"uid":124573,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"講到自己幾忙幾多理由，你男朋友夠忙啦，咪一樣做足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n調返轉佢無準備你咪一樣唔開心， 雖然你話就話無所謂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53973172b6b455cef19bf306368ac1cf3cbc295a","tid":968211,"uid":127283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:17:04.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"566bcb3d89e800e586e1f9961787ba6cd1575b86","tid":968211,"uid":51802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"遲早散<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條仔一定係毒撚仲要又淋"},{"pid":"1639aba62cbdf40b3e4f29bd07f3b9d23b2f4367","tid":968211,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"03e984962d413655a83405455a6a54d96a269540","tid":968211,"uid":15811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:20:04.000Z","msg":"買禮物係講你有冇心姐<br />\n忙唔忙係你比你自己既藉口多D，佢都會忙，但佢肯去買禮物比驚喜你<br />\n雖然佢未必有講佢想要咩禮物，但你可以買啲覺得岩佢用既野/小飾物都好"},{"pid":"bee4d4477bc07a1c7211ce823532cb733bbca83b","tid":968211,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"永遠淨係人哋對你好<br />\n你對人就連少少心思都唔肯花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ead7cda4d07071d1d0c504bf7d4a7ebcd37ec37","tid":968211,"uid":192325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"566bcb3d89e800e586e1f9961787ba6cd1575b86","tid":968211,"uid":51802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"遲早散<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條仔一定係毒撚仲要又淋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:29:20.000Z","msg":"佢個樣正正常常"},{"pid":"5ab7e34bf2acd71cd45a2434c03bb7aad2e5b597","tid":968211,"uid":192325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03e984962d413655a83405455a6a54d96a269540","tid":968211,"uid":15811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:20:04.000Z","msg":"買禮物係講你有冇心姐<br />\n忙唔忙係你比你自己既藉口多D，佢都會忙，但佢肯去買禮物比驚喜你<br />\n雖然佢未必有講佢想要咩禮物，但你可以買啲覺得岩佢用既野/小飾物都好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:30:46.000Z","msg":"佢都有咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122dfae6eca31e784e286d2988b1a5036063f9b9","tid":968211,"uid":51802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ead7cda4d07071d1d0c504bf7d4a7ebcd37ec37","tid":968211,"uid":192325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"566bcb3d89e800e586e1f9961787ba6cd1575b86","tid":968211,"uid":51802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"遲早散<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /